Total Deletions

This chart illustrates the total number of records deleted in each Assembly Constituency (AC). The color gradient represents the percentage of deleted records relative to the total records considered, highlighting constituencies with high deletion rates.

Net Deviation

This chart shows the net deviation in each AC, representing the variance from expected values. Positive or negative deviations indicate areas where deletions significantly differ from the average.
